Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:12.29,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Famous Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:23.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,20 more miles to Currie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.14,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So they want to get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:34.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.47,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Bring it down!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.01,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.98,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this sea breeze feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.70,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That family is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.98,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,with the heavy looking trunk\Nand the little medical bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.21,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,he must be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.28,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play more!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.41,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets hurt,\Njust bring him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a thick fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:22.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:35.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Sorry I surprised you.\NI'm Dr. Watson, and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:41.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes... Sherlock Holmes.\NI'm a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:48.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have had quite a few dangerous\Nexperiences in your line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:52.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I was working as an\Narmy surgeon in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A hard time there, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:08.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it requires a wide range of\Nknowledge to work as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:08.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an expert in botany,\Nchemistry and physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And I like to play violin very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:32.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing a symbol\Njust like that when I was in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! It's Bengal's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:37.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a symbol\Nof the Bengal Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you find this a little odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Straits of Dover,\N4000 miles from the Indian Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose the Bengal Pirates\Nare doing all the way over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them! It's them!\NThey followed me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:07:59.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to fear.\NPlease open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:30.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A private detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The people chasing after\Nyou are Bengal Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:51.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And what they're looking for\Nis hidden inside your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That black box...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And perhaps, your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:07.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:26.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,His heart has been weakened,\Nbut I don't think it's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:27.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:32.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We really wanted to have some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Since my father got that letter,\Nhe's been very nervous and frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been six months\Nsince we left on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know any of these four names?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:04.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the name my father\Nused when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Bengal Pirate,\Na long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The other three people\Nwere his associates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:15.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,now they're chasing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:18.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a shark's tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bengal Pirates have a custom\Nof sending a shark's tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,to announce the\Ndeath mark of a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:33.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the pirate ship is here to take\Nrevenge on Lord George?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Engineer! Stoke more coals!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye! Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:21.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:34.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:40.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll show no mercy!\NNow that they've targeted this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many\Npassengers on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get them involved\Njust because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:50.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time,\Nwe'd like to help you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:55.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, please fully explain\Nthe little box in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you already know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:17.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I took this box when I betrayed and\Nescaped from my three compatriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:29.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what they are trying to get,\Nin addition to my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't catch up with us\Nif we run this ship at full speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with the engine room?!\NStoke more coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,T... This?!\NDid they do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley! Are you rowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rowing brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume those two people\Nstopped the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are they pirates, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this back to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mr. Watson, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but what do\Nyou want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:32.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to collect\Nsmall and shiny objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it take long to repair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:50.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They completely destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stall for a little while,\Nbut please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:04.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going? Did you get enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:24.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move any closer, I will throw\Nthese jewels into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me? I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:43.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to throw any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it take much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping, but\Nit will take more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,W... wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hand over Lord George and the\Ntreasure, we won't harm anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Still not finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you giving us\Nthe treasure or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:13.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! I'll give it to you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, what's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to celebrate.\NWe have yet to find a way of escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you can lend\Nme a hand, Mr. Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:01.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My, this is a great motorcar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Lord George.\NHang a rope ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:55.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Watson, please take care\Nof the accelerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now comes the real fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We can escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shift your weight slowly,\Nall the way to the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:22.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:37.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The British Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they finally\Ngot through to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:50.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Inspector Lestrade\Nof Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:57.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:00.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture everybody for\Nthe honour of Scotland Yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:17.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley, row harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:18.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they're here to pick us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:31.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes! Mr. Watson!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shake hands again.
